    v1 = 0.0

    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(v2)
    v0 = wp.abs(v2)
    v1 = wp.exp((0.87 - (v0 + 0.37 - v0 + 0.68)))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(tmp + 0.10) / (tmp + 0.54 * v0 + 0.37)))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.35)
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.52)) / (v2 - 0.00))
    v2 = tmp
